<informationtext name="Information">
<![CDATA[
<p>The Arabic Minor allows students to achieve advanced proficiency in Arabic while learning about Arabic literature and culture. The Arabic Minor is open to undergraduates in all four colleges.</p>
<h2>Minor Advisor</h2>
<p><a href="https://mesa.ucdavis.edu/advising-office" target="_blank">Middle East/South Asia Studie</a><a href="https://mesa.ucdavis.edu/advising-office">s Advising Office</a></p>
]]>
</informationtext>
