<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>UC Davis currently offers three years of Arabic—elementary, intermediate, &amp; advanced levels. Students may request independent studies at more advanced levels. Instruction is in Modern Standard Arabic with a component of colloquial Arabic that integrates listening, speaking, reading, and writing.  Learning Arabic can be rewarding and useful as preparation for careers in the private, public or nonprofit sectors.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
